  "title": "Cleaner",
  "description": "<p>Job Responsibilities</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Dish washing duties.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Clear used dishes and utensils.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Clean and sanitize table tops, chairs, and surrounding areas.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Sweep, mop, and vacuum floors to maintain cleanliness.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Empty trash bins, clear rubbish, and ensure proper disposal.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Clean and maintain pantry, kitchen, and storage areas.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Refill and maintain cleaning supplies (soap, tissues, sanitizers, etc.).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Assist in general cleaning of toilets/restrooms when required.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Wipe windows, glass panels, and doors regularly.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Ensure overall cleanliness and hygiene standards are met at all times</p>",
